# Senior Living Complaint Management Software | Issuetrak
## Streamline Resident Requests & Maintenance for Senior Living Communities
Issuetrak's complaint management software makes it easy for residents to submit complaints or requests. Your team will track, manage, and resolve issues in one easy-to-use platform and ensure resident satisfaction.

